OL,3,CBy-election candidates revealed after
OL,4,Ccouncillor dies
OL,6,FSix by-election candidates have been
OL,7,Frevealed following the death of
OL,8,FReform's first Cornwall councillor,
OL,9,FKevin Towill.
OL,11,FCllr Towill died suddenly in February
OL,12,Fat the age of 46 after suffering from
OL,13,Fa brain tumour.
OL,15,FHe became Cornwall Council's first
OL,16,FReform UK councillor after defecting
OL,17,Ffrom the Conservatives in 2025.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
