OL,3,CBy-election candidates revealed after
OL,4,Ccouncillor dies
OL,6,FThe by-election to become the member
OL,7,Ffor the Newquay Porth and Tretherras
OL,8,Fdivision at Cornwall Council will be
OL,9,Fheld on Thursday 23 April.
OL,11,FThe candidates for the seat are:
OL,13,FFor more details on how to vote in the
OL,14,FNewquay by-election next month, see
OL,15,FCornwall Council's election page.
OL,17,FCredit: Lee Trewhela, LDRS
